Annotation Interface DomainObject

@Documented @DesignPattern(DOMAIN_LANGUAGE) @Retention(SOURCE) @Target(TYPE) public @interface DomainObject
Marks a class as a Domain Object.

A Domain Object represents a concept from the problem domain (business, scientific, or technical domain) and is used to model real-world entities inside the system.
